                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row hidden md:block -mx-2">
                    <a href="#" class="text-gray-800 rounded hover:bg-gray-900 hover:text-gray-100 hover:font-medium py-2 px-2 md:mx-2">Home</a>
                    <a href="#" class="text-gray-800 rounded hover:bg-gray-900 hover:text-gray-100 hover:font-medium py-2 px-2 md:mx-2">About</a>
                    <a href="#" class="text-gray-800 rounded hover:bg-gray-900 hover:text-gray-100 hover:font-medium py-2 px-2 md:mx-2">Contact</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
        <div class="flex bg-white" style="height:600px;">
            <div class="flex items-center text-center lg:text-left px-8 md:px-12 lg:w-1/2">
                <div>
                   <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-800 md:text-4xl">RentEase est votre solution <span class="text-indigo-600"><span class="text-green-600">tout-en-un pour simplifier la gestion de vos locations</span></span></h2>

                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500 md:text-base">Que vous soyez propriétaire d'une seule propriété ou d'un portefeuille immobilier étendu, RentEase vous offre les outils nécessaires pour gérer efficacement vos locations!</p>
                    <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-start mt-6">
                        <a class="px-4 py-3 bg-gray-900 text-gray-200 text-xs font-semibold rounded hover:bg-gray-800" href="/home">Voir plus</a>
                        <a class="mx-4 px-4 py-3 bg-gray-300 text-gray-900 text-xs font-semibold rounded hover:bg-gray-400" href="home/login">Se Connecter</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden lg:block lg:w-1/2" style="clip-path:polygon(10% 0, 100% 0%, 100% 100%, 0 100%)">
                <div class="h-full object-cover" style="background-image: url(https://luxury-houses.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/An-Unforgettably-Elegant-Delray-Beach-Home-for-Sale-23-768x511.jpg)">
                    <div class="h-full bg-black opacity-25"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
